FBIS4-4037 "drchi082_k_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-082 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Deng Xiaoping in `Intensive Care' at Military Hospital Deng Xiaoping in `Intensive Care' at Military Hospital Daughter Says Deng `Well,' `Resting' HK2804033094 Hong Kong AFP in English 0326 GMT 28 Apr 94 HK2804033094 Hong Kong AFP English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 28 (AFP) -- The daughter of China's paramount leader Deng Xiaoping Thursday denied rumours that her father's health was deteriorating, saying that he was well and resting at home. "My father is at home in Beijing and his state of health has not changed," Deng Lin told AFP at a fashion show here organised by top French designer Pierre Cardin.
